# Fortune Pump

**The retro crypto fortune teller built on Base.**

Insert 1$ or 10$ in USDC → press the button → the machine spins → you get a random shitcoin from the freshest pumps of the moment.

### Features
- Retro pixel + psychedelic aesthetic
- Blue Pepe Zoltar as your fortune teller
- Real on-chain USDC betting
- powered smart filters
- Built on Base

### Tech Stack
- Next.js 14
- TypeScript
- Wagmi + Viem
- Framer Motion (animations)
- Tailwind CSS

---

**"Insert coin. Spin your fate."**
